            </div>

            <div class="case-study-content">
                <div class="case-study-header">
                    <h3 class="case-study-title">Field Services Company</h3>
                    <p class="case-study-subtitle">Industrial Services & Operations</p>
                </div>

                <div class="case-study-grid">
                    <div class="case-study-column">
                        <div class="case-study-section">
                            <h4 class="case-label">The Problem</h4>
                            <ul class="case-list problem">
                                <li>Billing delayed by weeks due to manual spreadsheet workflows</li>
                                <li>No real-time visibility into job status or crew locations</li>
                                <li>Full-time employee dedicated to time card reconciliation</li>
                                <li>Revenue leakage from unbilled hours and materials</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="case-study-column">
                        <div class="case-study-section">
                            <h4 class="case-label">The Solution</h4>
                            <ul class="case-list solution">
                                <li>Custom mobile time clock with GPS verification</li>
                                <li>Automated approval workflows integrated with QuickBooks</li>
                                <li>Real-time job tracking dashboard</li>
                                <li>Automated billing generation from approved time</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="case-study-column">
                        <div class="case-study-section">
                            <h4 class="case-label">The Impact</h4>
                            <ul class="case-list impact">
                                <li><strong>Billing cycle reduced from weeks to days</strong></li>
                                <li><strong>Eliminated full-time spreadsheet position</strong></li>
                                <li><strong>Recovered significant unbilled time annually</strong></li>
                                <li>Real-time job profitability visibility</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="case-study-meta">
                    <div class="meta-item">
                        <span class="meta-label">Timeline</span>
