    <!-- FAQ Section -->
    <section id="faq" class="faq">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-header">
                <h2 class="section-title">Common Questions</h2>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-grid">
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3 class="faq-question">What makes you different from dev shops?</h3>
                    <p class="faq-answer">
                        We're not a development shop — we're an operations company that builds software. We've spent 20 years running IT operations, managing infrastructure, and solving real business problems. We understand operational efficiency, workflow design, and system integration from hands-on experience, not just technical implementation.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3 class="faq-question">Why not just use AI tools ourselves?</h3>
                    <p class="faq-answer">
                        Off-the-shelf AI tools solve generic problems. Your operational challenges are specific to your business processes, existing systems, and workflow requirements. We build custom platforms that integrate with your existing infrastructure and solve your exact problem — not a close approximation.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3 class="faq-question">What if we already have [Tool X]?</h3>
                    <p class="faq-answer">
                        Good. We integrate with it. Most of our projects involve connecting existing tools, filling gaps where commercial software doesn't fit, and building the "glue layer" between systems. We're not here to replace working tools — we solve problems your current stack can't handle.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3 class="faq-question">How do you price projects?</h3>
                    <p class="faq-answer">
                        Projects are priced based on measurable impact. If we can't identify significant annual impact (time savings, revenue recovery, cost reduction), we'll tell you upfront. Development happens in predictable phases with clear deliverables. No long-term contracts — just working software that solves real problems.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3 class="faq-question">What happens after deployment?</h3>
                    <p class="faq-answer">
                        Monthly ongoing services include infrastructure management, security updates, monitoring, and support. Your platform runs on SOC 2 certified infrastructure. We handle the technical operations so you can focus on using the system. Additional features are developed in predictable phases as needed.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3 class="faq-question">Do you work with companies outside Louisiana?</h3>
                    <p class="faq-answer">
                        Yes. While our roots are in Louisiana, we work with mid-market companies nationwide. Custom software development and operational automation don't require physical presence — we work remotely with clients across the US who have complex operational challenges.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

